            "id": 88828,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Semelhante à nomeação de variáveis e funções, existem algumas práticas comuns ao definir classes.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Person\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, name, age)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.name = name\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.age = age\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"teacher = Person(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Emily&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"24\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"98\" endIndex=\"104\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>Person</code> seguido de <code>Person</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Class name",
            "id": 89046,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Os nomes das classes geralmente têm a primeira letra em maiúscula e o restante em minúsculas, como com <code>Person</code> aqui.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Person\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, name, age)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.name = name\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.age = age\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"12\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>Person</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
