            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Assim como métodos fora de classes, você pode usar as funções embutidas e os recursos principais do Python.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Pie\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, flavor, ingredients)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.flavor = flavor\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.ingredients = ingredients\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print_ingredients\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" self.ingredients:    \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"      print(i)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"applePie = Pie(\" /><text value=\"'apple'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", [\" /><text value=\"'flour'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"'eggs'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"'apples'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"'butter'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"])\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"applePie.print_ingredients()\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"150\" endIndex=\"153\" /><option startIndex=\"154\" endIndex=\"155\" /><option startIndex=\"156\" endIndex=\"158\" /></options></int